{"konami_id": 9612, "password": 37926346, "name": {"en": "Steelswarm Roach", "de": "Stahlschar-Schabe", "es": "Cucaracha Horda de Acero", "fr": "Cafard Colonie de Chrome", "it": "Scarafaggio Brancoacciaio", "pt": "Barata Hordeum Ferro", "ja": "\u30a4\u30f3\u30f4\u30a7\u30eb\u30ba\u30fb\u30ed\u30fc\u30c1", "ja_romaji": "Inveruzu R\u014dchi", "ko": "\uc778\ubca8\uc988 \ub85c\uce58", "ko_rr": null, "zh-TW": "\u4fb5\u90aa\u8755 \u87d1\u8782", "zh-CN": "\u4fb5\u90aa\u8680\u871a\u880a"}, "text": {"en": "2 Level 4 monsters\nWhen a Level 5 or higher monster(s) would be Special Summoned (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card; negate the Special Summon, and if you do, destroy it.", "de": "2 Monster der Stufe 4\nWenn ein oder mehr Monster der Stufe 5 oder h\u00f6her als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung beschworen w\u00fcrden (Schnelleffekt): Du kannst 1 Material von dieser Karte abh\u00e4ngen; annulliere die Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung und falls du dies tust, zerst\u00f6re sie.", "es": "2 monstruos de Nivel 4\nCuando uno o m\u00e1s monstruos de Nivel 5 o mayor fueran a ser Invocados de Modo Especial (Efecto R\u00e1pido): puedes desacoplar 1 material de esta carta; niega la Invocaci\u00f3n Especial y, si lo haces, destr\u00fayela.", "fr": "2 monstres de Niveau 4\nLorsqu'un ou plusieurs monstres de min. Niveau 5 vont \u00eatre Invoqu\u00e9s Sp\u00e9cialement (Effet Rapide) : vous pouvez d\u00e9tacher 1 Mat\u00e9riel de cette carte ; annulez l'Invocation Sp\u00e9ciale, et si vous le faites, d\u00e9truisez-les.", "it": "2 mostri di Livello 4\nQuando uno o pi\u00f9 mostri di Livello 5 o superiore stanno per essere Evocati Specialmente (Effetto Rapido): puoi staccare 1 materiale da questa carta; annulla l'Evocazione Speciale e, se lo fai, distruggili.", "pt": "2 monstros de N\u00edvel 4\nQuando um ou mais monstros de N\u00edvel 5 ou mais seriam Invocados por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial (Efeito R\u00e1pido): voc\u00ea pode desassociar 1 mat\u00e9ria deste card; negue a Invoca\u